        "title": "Avoid retaining menu refresh state",
        "body": "## Summary\n- Avoid retaining `StatusItemController` and the open menu for the full Codex account-scoped refresh task.\n- Keep the existing phase-change callback guarded by weak captures so menu refreshes only run while the menu/controller still exist.\n\n## Proof\n- `swiftlint --strict Sources/CodexBar/StatusItemController+Menu.swift`\n- `swift build --build-tests 2>&1 | tee /tmp/codexbar-menu-capture-build.log`\n- `! rg -q \"ImplicitStrongCapture|weak ownership of capture\" /tmp/codexbar-menu-capture-build.log`\n\n## Notes\n- This is intentionally separate from the logging performance PR.\n",
